These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, indian
House: futuristic, townhouse
1. the indian is on the left or right of the dutch##3
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Nationality   | indian  | dutch |
| House       | futuristic | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret
2 different games are played: canasta, bridge
1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Pet   | hamster | ferret |
| Game      | bridge     | canasta  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, lawyer
1. the accountant is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food   | kale | papaya  |
| Job   | accountant | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, bus
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Transport   | bus | roller   |
| Game       | backgammon | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | documentary    |
| Sport   | surfing | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-6::.
